Scenario: Create a conference

POST /conferences

Scenario: Call for submissions

PUT /conferences/:id/call_for_submissions

Scenario: Submit a topic

POST /topics

Scenario: Shortlist a topic

GET /conferences/:id/topics

PUT /topics/:id/shortlist

Scenario: Unshortlist a topic

GET /conferences/:id/topics

PUT /topics/:id/unshortlist

Scenario: Add a track

GET /conference/:id/tracks

POST /conference/:id/tracks

Scenario: Add a session to a track

POST /tracks/:id/sessions